<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Jeevan</title>

    <style>
        body{
            background-color: lightblue;
            font-family: Cambria;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .container{
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1{
            color: darkblue;
        }

        h2{
            color: blue;
        }

        p{
            color: #003366;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Left Scrolling Text */
        .scroll-text{
            color: blue;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        /* Upward Scrolling Text */
        .scroll-up{
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid blue;
            width: 300px;
            height: 120px;
            margin: auto;
            color: blue;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 5px;
        }

        /* Grid Layout */
        .grid{
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2,180px);
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .box{
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid blue;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: blue;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Button */
        button{
            background: blue;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button:hover{
            background: darkblue;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer{
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: navy;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <h1>Welcome to Jeevan</h1>

    <!-- Left Scrolling Text -->
    <marquee class="scroll-text" direction="left">
        🌐 Welcome to Jeevan - Learn HTML and CSS with a Simple Website!
    </marquee>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>

    <p>
        Jeevan is a beginner-friendly website created using HTML and CSS.
        It demonstrates webpage design with colors, scrolling text,
        grid layouts, buttons, and simple styling techniques.
    </p>

    <h2>Latest Updates</h2>

    <!-- Upward Scrolling Text -->
    <marquee class="scroll-up" direction="up" scrollamount="2">
        ✔ Learn HTML Basics <br><br>
        ✔ Style pages using CSS <br><br>
        ✔ Create Grid Layouts <br><br>
        ✔ Design Attractive Webpages <br><br>
        ✔ Practice Web Development
    </marquee>

    <h2>Our Features</h2>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="box">HTML Basics</div>
        <div class="box">CSS Styling</div>
        <div class="box">Grid Layout</div>
        <div class="box">Scrolling Text</div>
    </div>

    <h2>About Jeevan</h2>

    <p>
        Jeevan is designed to help beginners understand the fundamentals
        of web development. It combines HTML for webpage structure and
        CSS for styling, making the webpage simple, attractive, and easy
        to understand.
    </p>

    <button onclick="alert('Welcome to Jeevan!')">Explore More</button>

    <div class="footer">
        © 2026 Jeevan | Designed using HTML & CSS
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
